description: First Hydrogen Corp. focuses on zero-emission vehicles, green hydrogen production and distribution, and supercritical carbon dioxide extractor systems. It is designing and building hydrogen-fuel-cell-powered light and medium commercial vehicle under two agreements with AVL Powertrain and Ballard Power Systems Inc. The company was formerly known as Pure Extraction Corp. and changed its name to First Hydrogen Corp. in October 2021. First Hydrogen Corp. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Balraj S. Mann BA. CA., CPA
